accessible, it's just that--

01:07:54.429 --> 01:07:56.220
-But it's just going
somewhere else, right?

01:07:56.220 --> 01:07:56.690
-Yeah.

01:07:56.690 --> 01:07:58.190
-It's not going to
the rocks, right?

01:07:58.190 --> 01:08:00.960
