01:08:03.670 --> 01:08:05.570
you have lots of ocean
water and sediment.

01:08:05.570 --> 01:08:09.030
But that, that's been
happening all the time.

01:08:09.030 --> 01:08:12.200
I think the deep water aquifers,
it's because we're using it up

01:08:12.200 --> 01:08:14.530
and we're pumping it
out into the oceans,

01:08:14.530 --> 01:08:15.840
into the river system.

01:08:15.840 --> 01:08:17.896
So it's being removed
from the land,

01:08:17.896 --> 01:08:19.479
and it's being pumped
into the oceans.

01:08:19.479 --> 01:08:20.840
And then going elsewhere.

01:08:20.840 --> 01:08:22.240
